{"Author": "Mohammad Subhan", "Date": "on May 9, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Works perfect with a lot of things", "Text": "Just bought a house so trying to automate a few things. This hub is the brain for most of the things ill be using. Works perfect with a lot of things."}
{"Author": "DStoneburner", "Date": "on May 7, 2018", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Pain to Upgrade", "Text": "Upgrading requires fully removing everything and deleting all data which requires reaching out to customer service."}
{"Author": "Shawn B", "Date": "on May 7, 2018", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "At first it was great", "Text": "At first this was great. It works well, and is easy to setup.\n\nThe software is easy to navigate, and has options for developers to create their own interfaces for any device they want.\n\nBut sadly it feels as if Samsung has given up on this and the application. They have not released a new version of hardware in years, and the device support has not added any new hardware in over a year. They still do not have official nest support.\nThey have added basic automation options other hubs have now mainly focused around colors.\n\nThey are also trying to convert people to use their new smart connect application, which has even less device support, and a less advanced automation system which limits what you can do with automations.\n\nI am not sure if samsung has given up on home automation or if they are trying to get users to buy only samsung harware."}
{"Author": "Geoffrey Fortier", "Date": "on May 6, 2018", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Quirky Toy, Not For Actual Use", "Text": "Amateurish and unreliable. Simply went offline and never came back. No amount of resetting helps, app simply says \"offline\" and online support is mostly other users asking each other about the same questions."}
{"Author": "TwizzY", "Date": "on May 6, 2018", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Otherwise it is easy to use and works flawlessly when everything is in ...", "Text": "Was very frustrating to setup because the App was in between migrations from Samsung and the original developer. Otherwise it is easy to use and works flawlessly when everything is in sync."}
{"Author": "Kevin", "Date": "on May 5, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Five Stars", "Text": "Simple and work well."}
{"Author": "Jumbo Gym", "Date": "on May 5, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great hub works with most smart devices.", "Text": "This may well be the best smart things hub out there. It talks with almost all smart devices (but not quite all) using its app on your phone/tablet/computer. Everything appears under its single ecosystem displayed on the app so you can manage everything from a single app. Anazon or Google will no doubt include this capability with their own built-in hubs soon, but for now, this is sweet."}
{"Author": "Rob D", "Date": "on May 4, 2018", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Worked great for about 10 months", "Text": "Worked great for about 10 months. I assume some update crippled the range, because now it can't reach Z-Wave outlets in the very next room (less than 30 feet away).\n\nThis product gets 1 star for not only failing to work, but ruining my whole investment in other Z-Wave tech."}
{"Author": "JinBok Lee", "Date": "on May 4, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Five Stars", "Text": "Good"}
{"Author": "Jerry Plyler", "Date": "on May 3, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Service service service thank you Michelle B.", "Text": "I would love to give a great big shout out to Michelle B Smarthings customer rep.. She was the best service rep. I think I have ever had the pleasure of talking to. I give the product 4 stars but the customer service makes it a 5 all day long. When you have such great customer Reps. like Michelle B. Samsung is doing something right. Its representatives like her that makes you feel good about buying their product. Its like the old saying goes its the service after the sale and boy did I get the service. Thank you so much Michelle B. because of your service you can bet I will buy Samsung Smarthings again and again."}
