{"Author": "Jay Saenz", "Date": "on May 1, 2018", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "The SmartThings Smart Home Hub is a great idea with two major ...", "Text": "The SmartThings Smart Home Hub is a great idea with two major drawbacks.\n\nThe Good:\nBeautiful Design\nThe Old App Words Well.\n\nThe Bad\nTerrible Range. I have a 1200 square foot open apartment and get frequent disconnects.\nThe new app is terrible\n\nMy recommendation is you look elsewhere at least until samsung gets it's app figured out."}
