{"Author": "Ryan H.", "Date": "on July 23, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "... to take time to review this hot pile of garbage. Literally nothing about it is consistent or reliable ...", "Text": "I never review things online but I'm going to take time to review this hot pile of garbage. Literally nothing about it is consistent or reliable in any form. Geofencing, automation, sensors, you name it--if you set something up with this hub be prepared for false positives or just plain confusion. It gets confused about who is home, what doors are open, whether there is motion, what time of day it is. Do. Not. Buy. This. Product."}
