{"Author": "Jim F", "Date": "on July 6, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "The \"Brain\" with no brains", "Text": "Bought this on sale at Best Buy for our new home. I believe (and hope) that this was a defective unit. It would not recognize the \"welcome code\" that came with it. Support was really no help at all. Tried multiple times (yes, with the correct code, thanks for you help support), and then finally, magically, it worked. Okay, I thought, that was nasty and unnecessary, but I'll keep trying. Set up ALL of my devices, got them labeled and ready to go. Then, WITH THE APP OPEN, the device reset itself. I lost everything I had spent the last hour or so getting set up. This is a return, I'm trying the Wink Hub 2 next..."}
