{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on January 15, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Really disappointed that the HUB requires a connection to some unknown ...", "Text": "Really disappointed that the HUB requires a connection to some unknown server outside of the home. They do not provide any software that I can install on my home PC to set up and control my home devices. I do not want to register with some outside entity to control my devices. Samsung provide no software at all in the box with the product. Why should anyone trust an outside unknown group to have control of home devices"}
{"Author": "T P", "Date": "on January 14, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Solid Hub", "Text": "I have this hub running zigbee connected bulbs, zwave switches and zwave smoke detectors. No issues at all with set routines or turning things on/Off via Alexa."}
{"Author": "Eric Paul", "Date": "on January 14, 2017", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Don't buy this if you have an Amazon echo and ...", "Text": "Don't buy this if you have an Amazon echo and more than one location. You will only be able to get Alexa to work with one location and apparently they have no plans to fix it."}
{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on January 13, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "It has been the best new addition to our house so far", "Text": "I am a first time home buyer and after a lot of research on different home security methods, I settled on Samsung SmartThings. It has been the best new addition to our house so far. Installation of the hub was quick and easy. The guide is intuitive and explains the different LED notifications for the hub in an easy-to-ready chart. I've had everything hooked up for about 1 1/2 months now and have never experienced a break in connectivity between any of my devices and the hub (2 motion sensors, 3 multipurpose sensors, 4 Arlo cameras, 1 Smart light bulb). The app is also a great user friendly feature and I use it to monitor my SmartThings devices along with other SmartThings compatible devices."}
{"Author": "Mike Mendoza", "Date": "on January 13, 2017", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Four Stars", "Text": "Really good product with lots of integrations. Really helped boost Alexa capabilities."}
