{"Author": "Boomer", "Date": "on December 28, 2016", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "We love Smartthings and have had no issues with this device", "Text": "We love Smartthings and have had no issues with this device. We love that the community creates custom ones like for the GE fan controller."}
