{"Author": "Tobor", "Date": "on December 28, 2016", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Works exceedingly well and it's easy to setup with iPad.", "Text": "Fantastic home automation device. It's easy to setup on any iPad or iPhone. If you have a decent internet connection the response time is quite acceptable. It runs all my lights without a hitch; through voice commands with Alexa."}
