{"Author": "Benjamin", "Date": "on December 17, 2016", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "A great addition to our home automation!", "Text": "So far this has been awesome. I've started building my SmartThings automation for a few weeks now. I've got this tied into my Logitech Harmony remote to automatically turn on and off the entertainment system, I can control my lights with it and the Harmony remote, and it's tied into my Honeywell thermostats to automatically adjust them when we go to bed, wake up, and when everyone's left the house (I'd do this by schedule, but our work schedules are crazy). Knowing that all the systems tie together and work as one has been awesome."}
